            dusted in a ghosting pattern that is rendered in @{"SHADOWPEN" LINK "gg:doc/NDK/Guide/Include/intuition/screens.h/File" 98}.

            Defaults to @{"FALSE" LINK "gg:doc/NDK/Guide/Include/exec/types.h/File" 98}.

