    NOTES

        This class is best suited for use in a ReAction layout group
        and requires receiving @{"GM_DOMAIN" LINK "gg:doc/NDK/Guide/Include/intuition/gadgetclass.h/File" 323} prior to the first @{"GM_RENDER" LINK "gg:doc/NDK/Guide/Include/intuition/gadgetclass.h/File" 302}
        in order to size & position its imagery correctly.

